* First of all i added Alcohol 120% with package , to install , for the users who doesn't have it yet .

1) install the alcohol 120% 
2) you can mount or burn the mdf file that included in the Folder " Pro_Flight "
3) after mount or burn , double click in the Cd , and then click in FGSsetup.exe
4) follow the installation , and then finish
5) run the game through the Desktop or the Start Menu 
6) Choose the Option that you want in your Air-Plane , And Begin to Fly .
